					<p class="mission-statement">GadgetFix was founded to bridge the gap between traditional repair shops and modern mobile lifestyles. We bring professional device repair directly to our customers throughout the Dallas-Fort Worth area.</p>
					
					<h3>Our Service Promise</h3>
					<p>We understand that mobile devices are essential to your daily life. When your phone breaks, you need it fixed quickly and correctly. Our certified technicians use high-quality parts and proven repair techniques to restore your device to perfect working condition.</p>
					
					<p>With over 500 successful repairs completed, we have built our reputation on reliability, transparency, and exceptional customer service. Every repair comes with a comprehensive 90-day warranty because we stand behind our work.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="story-image">
					<div class="image-placeholder">
						<div class="placeholder-icon">
							<svg role="img" aria-label="Expert technicians at work" width="80" height="80" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
